programme.title: Även anglar ater bonor
programme.desc: Fribrottaren Charlie (Bud Spencer) och drommaren Sonny (Giuliano Gemma) ar två fattiga tuffingar i 30-talets Chicago som hoppas på battre tider. De får chansen till stora pengar nar de borjar arbeta for en maffiaboss. Problemet ar att de ar alldeles for blodiga. De lånar ut pengar till fattiga istallet for att inkassera beskyddarpengar och driver hela tiden maffiabossen till vansinne. Till slut beslutar sig skurkarna for att undanroja Charlie och Sonny. Men de har glomt en sak - Charlies formidabla styrka sitter framst i navarna!

programme.title: Miami Supercops
programme.desc: Har kommer annu en actionspackad komedi från den dynamiska duon Hill och Spencer. I "Miami Supercops" ser vi våra hjaltar jaga både brottslingar och 20 miljoner dollar som stals vid ett rån for ett par år sedan. Vi får uppleva mord, forodelse och totalt kaos under deras jakt på bytet och rånarna - och naturligtvis får de hjalp av två snygga tjejer!

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Wild Target
programme.desc: En klumpig yrkesmordare blir foralskad i sitt offer och måste skydda henne från både sin egen organisation och polisen.

programme.title: Shockwave
programme.desc: Nar en massiv vulkanisk storm drabbar varlden forsoker geofysikern Kate Ferris overtyga forsvarsdepartementet att det inte ar ett naturligt fenomen. Det ar resultatet av ett seismiskt supervapen, kant som Hell Storm, som aktiverats. Kate måste komma på ett satt att stoppa chockvågen innan den hotar manskligheten.

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: Elektra
programme.desc: Marvels femme fatale; Elektra (Garner) bevisar att utseende kan doda nar den sexigaste actionhjalten någonsin bryter sig ut från serietidningssidorna till filmduken. I sitt nya uppdrag tvingas hon fatta ett odesdigert beslut i kampen mellan gott och ont!

programme.title: Legal Action
programme.desc: Stjarnadvokaten Casey McKay lockas till en liten stad av sin exfru for att forsvara hennes bror som står åtalad for att ha mordat en distriktsåklagare. Casey blottlagger en konspirationsharva som staller honom oga mot oga med mr Gates, stadens allra mest korrupte markexploator. En f.d. marinsoldat hjalper Casey i konflikten nar det står klart att han behover mer an sitt juridiska kunnande for att hålla sig vid liv och radda sin klient.

programme.title: Jumper
programme.desc: Av regissoren till The Bourne Identity kommer annu en extrem adrenalinchock som tanjer på fantasins begransningar… David Rice ar en ung man utan granser – en “jumper” – fodd med den markliga formågan att kunna teleportera sig sjalv vart som helst på jorden inom ett ogonblick. Nar David upptacker att det finns fler som honom sjalv kastas han plotsligt in mitt i ett forntida krig. Han jagas av en blodtorstig skara fanatiker, fast beslutna att utrota alla jumpers. Nu måste David anvanda sin mycket speciella gåva smart for att ha en chans att overleva…

programme.title: Ghost Rider - Spirit Of Vengeance
programme.desc: Eld ska med eld bekampas! Johnny Blaze kampar alltjamt mot sin forbannelse som djavulens prisjagare. Och nar en hemlig religios sekt vill anlita hans tjanster, kanner han sig inte redo att annu en gång iklada sig Ghost Riders brinnande krafter och makt. Men kanske ar detta den sista mojligheten att gora sig fri från djavulens forbannelse en gång for alla!

programme.title: Instrument of War
programme.desc: Den amerikanska piloten Clair Cline blir nedskjuten och hamnar i fångenskap i norra Tyskland. En kamp tar slut, en annan tar vid – att hålla hoppet vid liv trots taggtråd och fortryck. Cline och hans medfångar måste hitta ett satt att hålla ihop, inte bara for att overleva utan aven for att utharda fångenskapen. Baserad på sanna handelser.

programme.title: Survivor
programme.desc: Survivor ar en thriller om en av det amerikanska utrikesdepartementets sakerhetsexperter som får en tjanst vid USA:s ambassad i London. Hennes jobb ar att stoppa terrorister från att ta sig in i USA och det placerar henne direkt i skottlinjen. Dodshotad, oskyldigt brottsanklagad, vanhedrad och på flykt måste hon till varje pris komma på hur hon ska rentvå sig och samtidigt stoppa en omfattande terrorattack som ar planerad att aga rum under nyårsfirandet vid Times Square i New York.

programme.title: Blood And Bone
programme.desc: Isaiah Bone (Michael Jai White) ar en skicklig mastare i kampsport. Efter fem år bakom galler skall han nu ut i verkligheten och borja ett nytt liv. Han anlander till Los Angeles dar ingen vet vem han ar och dar overraskar han alla genom att slåss som en varldsmastare. På gatorna i LA ar det gangsterkungen James som styr och Bone tar sig snart an utmaningen att forsoka storta honom. Men Bone doljer en mork hemlighet och han ar dessutom ute efter hamnd. Bone upptacker snart att han måste slåss for sitt liv. Allt står på spel! EN VISUELLT BLÄNDANDE ACTIONFILM MED MICHAEL JAI WHITE (’Spawn’), JULIAN SANDS (’24 timmar’) OCH NONA GAYE (’Matrix Reloaded’).

programme.title: Dangerous Man
programme.desc: Efter 15 år bakom galler ar oskyldigt domde Shane Daniels åter en fri man. Men nar han blir vittne till en blodig uppgorelse dar den ryska maffian ar inblandad, kastas Shane in i ett brutalt gisslandrama. Med den nyvunna friheten som insats måste han kampa mot skrupulosa gangstrar for att radda en oskyldig flickas liv...

programme.title: Texas Killing Fields
programme.desc: Mellan 1983 och 1991 hittas fyra kvinnokroppar på samma plats i en stad i Texas. The Fields ar den sanna historien om en mans trettioåriga kamp for att losa mordgåtan, i det forgiftade oljelandskapet som kallas for Killing Fields.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Det hela borjar med att en magisk spira transporterar deras goda van April genom tid och rum, anda till samurajernas Japan. Leonardo och ganget ger sig genast av efter henne, och måste nu besegra den elake Lord Naringa for att radda den insparrade April och återta spiran som lorden kommit over. Annars lar de bli fast i medeltida Japan i eviga tider. Och dar finns ju inte ens några pizzerior…

programme.title: Skurkar och banditer
programme.desc: Tony Roma (Tomas Milian) ar alla tiders halaste gigolo, en sol-och-vårare och skojare specialiserad på att knycka formogna hemmafruars diamanter. Till slut kopplas den hemliga polisen Parker (Bud Spencer) in for att ta fast den lille skojaren. Parker vill helst åka på semester med sin stora familj. Istallet tvingas han nu skydda Tony sedan denne blivit vittne till ett maffiamord. Sjalvklart haglar råsoparna och smockorna nar Parker tar sig an maffiaganget och kastar skurkarna rakt igenom dorrar och vaggar.

programme.title: Spaghettiman
programme.desc: Clark saknar empati for allt och alla. Han skiter fullstandigt i varlden vi lever i och bryr sig knappt om sig sjalv heller. Men efter en incident med en gammal gryta fylld av spaghetti och en trasig mikro går nått fullstandigt snett. Clark forvandlas till en superhjalte som kan bekampa kriminalitet med hjalp av spaghetti. Men det finns en hake, du måste betala honom.

programme.title: Raining in the Mountain
programme.desc: I ett buddhisttempel i Mingdynastins Kina ar det dags for abboten att utse sin eftertradare. Men bland kandidaterna finns det de som framst ar ute efter att stjala den ovarderliga skriften i templets skattkammare. Intriger och allianser uppstår nar personliga ambitioner och andliga stravanden kolliderar.

programme.title: Final Shot
programme.desc: Lonnmordaren Frank har lagt sitt tidigare arbete på hyllan och forsoker leva ett till synes vanligt liv tillsammans med flickvannen och hans dotter. En dag kommer en okand maffia boss forbi for att få Franks hjalp att ha ihjal den som tagit livet av hans unga dotter. For att inte dra in sin egen familj i eventuella komplikationer måste Frank fatta ett beslut om att gora stoten åt bossen eller få ro med sin egen sjal?

programme.title: Shockwave
programme.desc: Nar en massiv vulkanisk storm drabbar varlden forsoker geofysikern Kate Ferris overtyga forsvarsdepartementet att det inte ar ett naturligt fenomen. Det ar resultatet av ett seismiskt supervapen, kant som Hell Storm, som aktiverats. Kate måste komma på ett satt att stoppa chockvågen innan den hotar manskligheten.

programme.title: Joyride
programme.desc: Jon ar en forkrossad men andå charmig odugling i nastan allt han foretar sig, Luke ar en mastare på att kora bil och på flykt från sitt forflutna och Keira ar drive-thru-bitrade på ett burgerstalle och veganaktivist. Tillsammans bildar de tre en trio tillfalliga banditer nar de reser genom hela Nya Zeeland i en "lånad" gul Mini Cooper och ifrågasatter samhallets likriktning och jagar forlorad karlek med ett massivt polisuppbåd och varsta mediacirkusen hack i hal.

programme.title: Fungi
programme.desc: Ett fartfyllt aventyr som staller vetenskap och naturlig balans mot kortsiktigt tankande i en kamp for mansklighetens overlevnad.

programme.title: Daredevil
programme.desc: Mot DAREDEVIL - Marvels legendariske superhjalte, kand som Mannen utan fruktan. Med spektakulara specialeffekter, slagsmålsscener utver det vanliga och nonstop action. På dagtid arbetar den blinde Matt Murdock som advokat, på natten ar han DAREDEVIL. En maskerad hjalte som bevakar stadens morka grander.

programme.title: The Fourth Musketeer
programme.desc: På uppdrag av sin far reser den unge dArtagnan från landsbygden i Gascogne till Paris, dar han blir indragen i en listig och mycket komplicerad komplott mellan kungens musketorer och kardinal Richelieus gardister. Blod ska spillas, och den som inte ar på sin vakt kommer få satta livet till.

programme.title: Immortals
programme.desc: Efter att de grekiska krigarna till slut vunnit over Titanerna, dyker ett nytt hot upp mot dem. Med enorm kraft, deklarerar Kung Hyperon krig mot hela manskligheten. Med sin blodtorstiga och vansinniga arme soker Hyperion genom Grekland efter den legendariske Epirus båge, ett vapen med obeskrivlig kraft, som smidits i himlen av sjalvaste Ares sjalv. Om vapnet hamnar i kungens ago, kan det forgora hela manskligheten, till och med forinta gudarna. Men de forntida lagarna forbjuder gudarna att ingripa i manskliga konflikter och gudarna forblir maktlosa mot Hyperion och hans arme.

programme.title: Snedseglarna
programme.desc: Alan (Terence Hill) ar en obotlig gambler som en dag spelar bort maffians pengar och måste fly for livet. Han hinner dock få med sig sin farbrors hemliga skattkarta och gommer sig på jordenruntseglaren Charlies (Bud Spencer) båt. Alan trixar med kompassen och snart når det udda paret den paradisiska soderhavso dar skatten ar nedgravd.Har finns emellertid också fientliga infodingar, manniskojagare och en japan som fortfarande tror att andra varldskriget pågår for fullt. Alan och Charlie slåss mot dem alla och har de ingen annan att fightas mot — ger de sig på varandra! Det farsartade aventyret ”Snedseglarna” visas nu for forsta gången i oklippt originalversion.

programme.title: Miami Supercops
programme.desc: Har kommer annu en actionspackad komedi från den dynamiska duon Hill och Spencer. I "Miami Supercops" ser vi våra hjaltar jaga både brottslingar och 20 miljoner dollar som stals vid ett rån for ett par år sedan. Vi får uppleva mord, forodelse och totalt kaos under deras jakt på bytet och rånarna - och naturligtvis får de hjalp av två snygga tjejer!

programme.title: Gun
programme.desc: Vapenrelaterat våld och en skenande brottsstatistik får polisen i Detroit att tillsammans med FBI starta ett fullskaligt krig mot stadens vapensmugglare. Rich och hans organisation blir de framsta måltavlorna for operationen. Och då Rich, hans baste van Angel, och hans alskarinna och leverantor Gabriella råkar ut for en affarsuppgorelse som går fel, avslojas en stor hemlighet som skakar Rich anda in i margen. Det blir hogexplosiv action med bland annat Val Kilmer, Curtis ”50 Cent” Jackson och Danny Trejo!

programme.title: New Life
programme.desc: Baby animals beguile with their innocent charm. But while some remain harmless, others have a deep-rooted instinct. It may take weeks or months of training to hone their skills. Their landscapes and lifestyles maybe very different, but these babies are born to hunt.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E02 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Kinabatangan River: Borneo – Forgotten Paradise
programme.desc: In Sabah, northern Borneo, flows the 560km-long Kinabatangan River. Nowhere else in Sabah are wild animals as easily spotted as along this river: orangutans, elephants, crocodiles, and proboscis monkeys. However, biodiversity is threatened as more rainforest gives way to palm oil plantations. Wildlife ventures into inhabited areas in search of food, leading to conflicts. Locals are fighting to preserve the rainforest and its unique wildlife, demonstrating that conservation and prosperity can coexist even in a modern society.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Pu Mat National Park: Vietnam – Of Bears and Men
programme.desc: The jungle in northern Vietnam is nearly impenetrable, with some areas never touched by humans. The remote rainforests of Pu Mat National Park serve as a refuge for endangered wildlife such as black bears, monkeys, and pangolins. Tuan, a biologist and bear specialist, embarks on an expedition to these untouched regions of the park in search of bears. The most hunted animal here is the pangolin, sought after for its scales believed to have medicinal properties and its meat considered a delicacy. A small Vietnamese conservation organization fights for the survival of this species.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Gaoligongshan Park: China – Himalaya’s Gold
programme.desc: The Great Gobi National Park in southwestern Mongolia shelters one of the last populations of wild Bactrian camels, amid its ancient and mysterious desert landscape. With around 800 critically endangered animals, the Gobi remains one of the worlds most sparsely inhabited and inhospitable regions, yet its allure is undeniable, offering a captivating backdrop for encounters with wild camels and stories of people deeply connected to nature.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E05 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Great Gobi National Park: Mongolia – Following the Wild Camels
programme.desc: The jungle in northern Vietnam is nearly impenetrable, with some areas never touched by humans. The remote rainforests of Pu Mat National Park serve as a refuge for endangered wildlife such as black bears, monkeys, and pangolins. Tuan, a biologist and bear specialist, embarks on an expedition to these untouched regions of the park in search of bears. The most hunted animal here is the pangolin, sought after for its scales believed to have medicinal properties and its meat considered a delicacy. A small Vietnamese conservation organization fights for the survival of this species.

programme.title: Faroe Islands - A Secret Beauty
programme.desc: The Faroe Islands in the North Atlantic, located in the middle of the Gulf Stream between Scotland and Iceland, are an archipelago of eighteen green volcanic islands where a unique culture has developed over the last thousand years. As direct descendants of the Vikings, the Faroese feel committed to their traditions and hold on to customs, without missing out on the advantages of the modern and globalised world - from archaic hunter and shepherd culture to contemporary art. With the highest birth rate in Europe and the lowest social inequality in the world, the just fifty thousand Faroese are a very special people living on one of the last natural paradises in Europe.

programme.title: mareTV: The white wilderness in Greenlands East
programme.desc: Fjords, glaciers and the highest mountains in the Arctic: East Greenland with its spectacular nature is one of the most sparsely populated regions on earth. The people here live in extreme isolation and depend on helicopter flights for their supplies. Despite harsh conditions, the inhabitants here lovingly maintain their traditions and enjoy their outdoor leisure time even at minus 20 degrees Celsius. The town of Tasiilaq is the "metropolis" with 4,000 inhabitants and offers a very special attraction: the only ski lift on the east coast. Thomas Mikaelsen, the lift attendant, is not to be envied for his job. The only 100 meter long lift comes from Switzerland and is already 20 years old....

programme.title: Magical Moors
programme.desc: Wide open heaths, windswept and barren in winter, are transformed into wonderful carpets of white, fluffy cotton grass in summer. Large bears and wolves roam alongside delicately fluttering butterflies, the bubbling calls of black grouse and the enchanting trills of the great snipe. Moors, bogs and wetlands can be found all over in Europe. Everyone has at least heard about this habitat but most know little about it. It is an ancient yet largely unknown set of landscapes that is full of enchanting surprises. On a warm spring day, poisonous adders emerge from hiding to perform their impressive mating dance. As dusk falls, snipe gather on traditional leks, leaping and singing to impress the...

programme.title: The Sudheide - Woods, meadows, open country
programme.desc: Forests and fields, moors and heathland, shepherds and sheep - these are the symbols of an ostensibly unspoilt landscape that has inspired poets and painters alike for centuries. The secret of the almost 500 km² nature reserve Naturpark Sudheide lies in its diversity: the origins of its soil, geology and topography can be traced back to the ice age. But the region between Hamburg and Hannover is anything but unspoilt. For centuries, it was synonymous with heathland farmers and formed as a North German cultivated landscape. This documentary tells of an almost unknown region, which has been strongly influenced by mankind for centuries, yet still remains diverse in its nature. Nature...

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Wild Life, Gentle Nature
programme.desc: As contrasting as the landscapes of the 15th meridian east, so different are its animal inhabitants. What are the living conditions like in the heat of the Namibian Damaraland, in Lusatia or on the coast of Norway? Which challenges do elephants, whales or kingfishers have to master together with their companions from north to south?

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.desc: Almost 11000 kilometres lie between the northernmost and southernmost point of the 15th meridian east. Here you will find extreme landscapes such as the shimmering heat of Africa or the eternal cold of northern Scandinavia. Five people from Spitsbergen, Namibia, Slovenia, Germany and Poland dedicate their lives to environmental protection.

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Sow, Harvest, Eat – Our Conservatory
programme.desc: This episode focuses on people from five countries who share a common passion: The production of their own food and food. What culinary treasures are hidden in the different regions, from Spitsbergen to Sweden, Austria, Poland and Chad?

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 From Generation to Generation
programme.desc: The journey leads from the Norwegian Vesterålen to Chad, the Aeolian Islands and the Polish Giant Mountains. As different as the landscapes and cultures may be, all people are united in their love for their children and their desire to give something to tomorrows generation.

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.desc: What ideas are people on the 15th meridian east developing to shape the future and leave tomorrows generations a home worth living in? This consequence leads us to four future designers. From the barren Namib Desert to the glacier worlds of Spitsbergen, Sicily and the Croatian Mediterranean.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Gir National Park: India – Asia’s Last Lion
programme.desc: In the far west of India, unexpected predators roam: lions. Living freely in a human-inhabited area without fences, they occasionally prey on the livestock of the indigenous Maldhari people, who nevertheless take pride in sharing their region with these lions—a unique coexistence of humans and predators. In northern Gujarat, desert landscapes dominate, where semi-nomadic communities breed a unique camel breed capable of swimming: Karai camels swim up to 3km daily to mangrove islands for grazing.

Five people from Spitsbergen, Namibia, Slovenia, Germany and Poland dedicate their lives to environmental protection.

programme.title: King of the Mountains - Golden Eagle
programme.desc: Aerial shots of mating Golden eagles, a clash between a Golden and a White-tailed eagle, and an intimate glimpse into their nesting grounds combine to create a spectacular film. Tracking these majestic birds reveals the wild nature of their hunting grounds, showcasing the diverse animal and plant life that share their habitat with the king of the skies. Viewers are brought up close as the eagle effortlessly glides over forests and canyons, abruptly diving in a breathtaking pursuit of prey. Witnessing these birds in their natural habitats is witnessing them at their finest. Embark on a magnificent journey through the skies and landscapes with us.

programme.title: King of the Seas - Sea Eagle
programme.desc: The times where eagles have been seen as varmints are over. They are now perceived as an integral part of the food cycle. Due to the fact that the habitats of the sea eagles in Germany are largely found in the north-eastern regions that are rich in water, the movie accompanies the eagles to an island, home to hundreds of sea ravens, where they rob the baby sea ravens of their food. They seem to always profit from the successes of the fellow creatures in their habitats. This film introduces you to the expert poachers of the animal kingdom.

programme.title: Leap Of The Lynx
programme.desc: On the Iberian Peninsula, primeval landscapes are practically non-existent, so the Iberian lynx has lived on cultivated land for centuries – cattle, horse and pig pastures, cork oak forests, timberland, and even holy sites of pilgrimage. The diversity and beauty of these locations are truly stunning and their character and history as relevant to this story as that of the big cat itself. Until five years ago, both populations of Iberian lynx were quickly fading away. Their fragmented habitats were shrinking even further, they were starved by lack of prey and reduced by epidemics. But now, local authorities, scientists, landowners, and other groups have finally begun to act in unison.

programme.title: Bear Essentials
programme.desc: We follow three young bears of different species – polar bears, brown bears and sloth bears (like Baloo, the Jungle Book Bear) – that inhabit dramatically varied landscapes as they find their way in the world. We look at how their mothers teach them the skills they need to survive and watch the many dangers they face. Their young lives are full of learning, moments of great tenderness and life-threatening drama. Over three years all of our bears, despite hardships and losses along the way, prove they have what it takes, they all have learned their bear essentials.

programme.title: Wild Moments
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Moments: Dangerous and Deadly I
programme.desc: Wildlife film-makers often risk life and limb trying to capture unique images of their dangerous protagonists. In Alaska a cunning grizzly threatens the son of Andreas Kieling, on the remote Wrangel Island in northern-east Siberia his colleague Uwe Anders is taken by surprise by a a polar bear, and off the coast of South Africa a diving-team is unexpectedly surrounded by white sharks. But the life of the film-makers is also threatened by elemental forces, life-threatening diseases and failing technical equipment: Deep in the vast rainforests of West Africa cameraman Klaus Scheurich nearly dies of malaria, and in South India a film team narrowly escapes death in a hot-air balloon accident....

programme.title: Wild Moments
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Wild Moments: Dangerous and Deadly II
programme.desc: Wildlife filmmakers often risk life and limb trying to capture unique images of their dangerous protagonists. A cunning grizzly grabs a salmon off Andreas Kielings fishing rod, in the depths of the Amazon River a diving team has a spooky encounter with piranhas, in the Mediterranean Sea the currents nearly push Thomas Behrend into the mouths of angry sperm whales defending a newborn - and cameramen who want to film jaguars in the dense jungle of South America become easy prey for the well camouflaged cats. The life of the film-makers is also threatened by elemental forces and failing technical equipment: In the swamps of North Australia violent storms hold up the crossing of tearing...

programme.title: Wild Moments
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Wild Moments: Dangerous and Deadly III
programme.desc: Wildlife filmmakers often risk life and limb trying to capture unique images of their dangerous protagonists. In the Kruger National Park Josef Jozefowicz steps into a lionesses den to film her cubs, in Alaska Andreas Kieling mingles with giant elk bulls in order to film them in action, and in Florida his colleague Zoltan Torok gets very close to an alligator mother guarding its nest. The life of the film-makers is also threatened by elemental forces, and failing technical equipment: the strong and tearing current of the Yukon River throws Andreas Kielings boat onto a gravel bank, in the Democratic Republik of Congo camerawoman Heike Grebe is separated from her colleagues in the dense...

programme.title: Moksgmol - The Quest for the Spirit Bear
programme.desc: A forest that lives off fish, a white bear that is not a polar bear, and wolves that feed off the ocean… Canada’s Great Bear Rain Forest is a strange and pristine world, a land that time almost forgot. The awe-inspiring northern coastline of British Columbia with its great fjords that rival those in Norway, is the habitat of numerous species and the scene for the amazing co-existence of wolves, ravens, salmon, bears and a mystical rainforest, whose lives are intricately intertwined…

programme.title: The Moose Detective
programme.desc: Moose are an iconic species and of great importance to Sweden. That is why the country counts on a very special expert - the moose detective. Recently, a problem has developed on Öland regarding its moose. For a few years now on the island, the moose calves have been dying shortly after birth. Its a mystery. Every effort is made to save them. The island has called upon the moose detective to investigate. He follows several leads. Soon one of the suspects is identified - climate change. But it is not easy to convict the culprit. There are other suspects as well, the food shortage for example. Maybe they have joined hands as accomplices. In Sweden moose are very important. They are game...

programme.title: Search for the Ghost Bears
programme.desc: Our film journey begins in Alaskas west. We are hoping to find glacier bears in the glacial regions of the Katmai National Park on the Douglas River. At the end of July, brown bears have now arrived to fish for salmon. In the surrounding forests, grizzlies look for berries and fresh, green twigs. The Katmai is Alaskas most volcanic area, and with 15 active volcanoes it is a veritable powder keg, surrounded by glaciers. In the Hook glacier region moose and lynx accompany us. Bald eagles have arrived at the glacial boundary and begin to tear apart their freshly caught prey. At last, we catch sight of a glacier bear. Hungry, he has left the ice region and has been forced down here in...

programme.title: A Winters Tale - The Journey of the Snowy Owls
programme.desc: Snowy owls live a life full of mystery up in the Arctic. Thousands of years ago, they built a community of fate with their neighbors – lemmings. About every four years, lemmings proliferate in huge numbers. This way, snowy owls have enough feed for their young. The owls lay up to eleven eggs and can successfully raise the chicks – each of them needs two to four lemmings per day. Lately, however, lemmings’ mass reproduction hasn’t been as regular in some parts of the Tundra. What will happen to them and the snowy owls? What is the ecological link here? And what will happen if one year the winter arrives way too early? The best way for many birds to adapt to the winter is to flee to the...

programme.title: Survival of the Fittest in the Alps
programme.desc: The documentary shows the survival strategies of various animal species in the high mountains of the Alps in winter. Despite freezing temperatures and limited food supply, chamois, red deer and snow hares manage to survive the cold months. Latest research reveals the amazing abilities the animals have developed to adapt to the extreme conditions and also how climate change is altering the behaviour of the alpine inhabitants.

programme.title: Secret Life Of Deer
programme.desc: 30 million white-tailed deer live in the United States. They have begun to adapt themselves to living in a world of traffic, pets and backyards. In Cayuga Heights, New York, the suburb’s residents are trying to get used to this exceptional living arrangement. The deer can be spotted daily from kitchen windows and porches. Life in the suburbs is deer heaven – large areas of grass, no predators and plenty of water means their population is on a steady rise. In this documentary, white-tailed deer are outfitted with special cameras to take the viewer into their world. Deercam allows us to see them in a new light – not frozen in the headlights of a car or as shy residents of the woods, but...

programme.title: Strandwolf
programme.desc: She moves through the seal colony on Namibia’s wild Skeleton Coast with purpose and focus, gingerly stepping around the adults who snap at her heels. She’s searching for smaller prey. Following her is a young German field scientist, Ingrid Wiesel, who has now spent 17 years with Tosca’s clan; tracking, observing, and learning everything she can about one of the world’s least understood and most unusual predators.

Their young lives are full of learning, moments of great tenderness and life-threatening drama. programme.title: Moksgmol - The Quest for the Spirit Bear
programme.desc: A forest that lives off fish, a white bear that is not a polar bear, and wolves that feed off the ocean… Canada’s Great Bear Rain Forest is a strange and pristine world, a land that time almost forgot. programme.desc: Moose are an iconic species and of great importance to Sweden. That is why the country counts on a very special expert - the moose detective. Recently, a problem has developed on Öland regarding its moose. For a few years now on the island, the moose calves have been dying shortly after birth. Its a mystery. Every effort is made to save them. The island has called upon the moose detective to investigate. He follows several leads. Soon one of the suspects is identified - climate change. But it is not easy to convict the culprit. There are other suspects as well, the food shortage for example. Maybe they have joined hands as accomplices. In Sweden moose are very important. They are game...

programme.title: Search for the Ghost Bears
programme.desc: Our film journey begins in Alaskas west. We are hoping to find glacier bears in the glacial regions of the Katmai National Park on the Douglas River. At the end of July, brown bears have now arrived to fish for salmon. In the surrounding forests, grizzlies look for berries and fresh, green twigs. The Katmai is Alaskas most volcanic area, and with 15 active volcanoes it is a veritable powder keg, surrounded by glaciers. In the Hook glacier region moose and lynx accompany us. Bald eagles have arrived at the glacial boundary and begin to tear apart their freshly caught prey. At last, we catch sight of a glacier bear. programme.title: mareTV: Sardinia - Magical Island in the Mediterranean
programme.desc: Sardinia is the second-largest island in the Mediterranean. The Sardin-ians themselves say its a "continent for itself", a virtual world of its own, full of magic: A beach, gleaming in unreal pink shades, red corals protect against the evil eye and the inhabitants seem to remain forever young. On Sardinia, the owners of luxury yachts adopt sheep, fish have gold in their bellies and a giant mussel supplies the material for legendary sea silk. No one is surprised, that the Madonna goes on a sea cruise once a year.

programme.title: Italy My Love

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Night of Horror at Devils Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case) - On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her little sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Mysterious Murder at the Farm (Valerie Bary Case)- On Friday, March 26, 2004, in the region of Dijon, Laurent Bary came home from his work to discover the lifeless body of his wife, Valerie, bathing in a pool of blood. According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. The couple are going through a divorce, but this mother would never have left her seven children alone! An extensive search is undertaken but the woman cannot be found. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. A maniac inspired by a horror movie? Investigators soon find that the young girl felt she was being watched, and even threatened...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: In the early hours of the morning, Mathilde Croguennec, 18, attending "Teknival" in Brittany, is found at the foot of a tree with her throat cut. Investigators face the task of finding the killer from among the 43,000 participants of this huge open-air festival of electronic music, where drink and drugs are consumed in abundance. An unusual investigation that leads the police down a number of false avenues.

programme.desc: Arriving at her work, the secretary of a small firm in the suburbs of Geneva finds the body of Jean-Raymond Blatti, the companys new accountant. programme.desc: After the Permian period, the epic saga of evolution and extinction on Earth produced the worlds first dinosaurs, plesiosaurs and pterosaurs.

programme.title: The Cretaceous
programme.desc: Magnificent and terrifying dinosaurs like Triceratops and Tyrannosaurus ruled the land. But they were all wiped out in an instant by a collision with an asteroid!

programme.title: The Ordovician
programme.desc: For nearly 4 billion years, the continents of Earth were lifeless. But during the Ordovician, there was an explosion of life beneath the sea. Many creatures evolved.

programme.title: The Devonian
programme.desc: Life in the sea rebounded with a vengeance in the Devonian. Dozens of monstrous predators emerged, like the 40-foot long Dunkleosteus.

programme.title: Alien Life
programme.desc: Scientists investigate microbes found in Yellowstone National Parks thermal pools to understand the biology necessary for life at high temperatures.

programme.title: Frozen Archeology
programme.desc: There are places in Greater Yellowstone where the snow never melts, or at least, it never used to. Climate change is causing Yellowstone’s ice patches to recede.

programme.title: The Petrified Forest
programme.desc: Greater Yellowstone sits on top of a volcanic hot spot where devastating geological events unfolded. The result? A bizarre cemetery of fossilized forests.

programme.title: Mammoth Country
programme.desc: The Greater Yellowstone Area was once a rich grazing ground for huge Columbian mammoths. Now it’s a prime hunting ground for paleontologists and archaeologists.

programme.title: The Last Triceratops
programme.desc: Montana’s Hell Creek Formation is home to a trove of late Cretaceous fossils unlike any other in the world, revealing the last days of the great dinosaurs.

programme.title: Past and Future Yellowstone
programme.desc: Craters of the Moon National Monument is desolate – but 2,200 years ago, it was the site of today’s Yellowstone Hotspot, known for violent eruptions and huge craters.

programme.title: Worlds Best Dinosaur Fossil
programme.desc: An extraordinary new discovery of a dinosaur fossil so pristine and complete, that it shows off the texture, patterns, and color of a prehistoric giant. Discover this brand new species that roamed during the late Jurassic and Cretaceous periods.

programme.title: Recovering From Extinction

programme.title: Part 1: Rise of Civilization
programme.desc: In the region that includes the Mediterranean, the Aegean, Mesopotamia and Egypt, the Bronze Age arrived about 3000 BC and lasted nearly 2000 years. What singled out this period and the new societies and cities that emerged? The development of formal writing is one among several important factors.

programme.title: Part 2: Masters Of Trade
programme.desc: Trade, and in particular trade in luxury goods, drove the commerce economies of the Bronze Age. This is the time when the first super powers in history, Egypt and Mesopotamia, emerge and dominate the "world" stage of the Mediterranean and Aegean seas and surrounding areas.

programme.title: Part 3: Conquest And Collapse
programme.desc: The Bronze Age had the first large urban centers, powerful kingdoms and armies, writing, and trade routes across vast areas. What led to the collapse of the city-state entities and the end of the Bronze Age? Possibly a perfect storm of uncontrollable factors that are still being researched.

programme.title: Pierce Arrow
programme.desc: 1913 38C Brougham - "built up to a standard, not down to a price" - was worth the value of several houses at the time, with the special cachet of being the first car owned by the White House.

programme.title: Duesenberg
programme.desc: The 1930 Model J Duesenberg was the pinnacle of automotive engineering in power and speed, holding records not surpassed until the 1960s.

programme.title: Terraplane
programme.desc: The Hudson Terraplane 1937 Series 72 was a fast and affordable car with unique style and innovative design. The company, unlike others, survived the Depression.

programme.title: Corvette
programme.desc: The 1963 Split-Window Stingray Coupe combined power, performance, precision and youthful design.

programme.title: Oldsmobile
programme.desc: The Oldsmobile F88 was a "dream car" of the GM Oldsmobile line, but the auto, despite its sophisticated, debonair styling, was destined never to see production.

programme.title: Mustang
programme.desc: The Ford Mustang Shelby GT-500 was born of the 1960s vibe and the racing experience of Carroll Shelby, who set speed records at Bonnevile salt flats.

programme.title: The Hunt for the Slave Ship Guerrero
programme.desc: A team of underwater archeologists searches for the remains of the Guerrero, an illegal slave ship sunk in battle off the coast of Florida.

programme.title: The Last Persian Shah
programme.desc: Shah Mohammad Reza Pahlavi would have been 100 years in October 2019. The Shahs story begins with good ideas and ideals and ends in bloody chaos.

programme.title: Radioactive Forest - 10 Years After
programme.desc: We look at the satoyama landscape ten years after the nuclear disaster at Fukushima Daiichi Power Plant which was followed by the 3.11 megaquake.

programme.title: Winged Creatures
programme.desc: På ett ogonblick forandras allt - hur går du vidare nar ditt liv slås i spillror? Det ar tidig morgon i Los Angeles, en psykopat skjuter besinningslost ihjal ett antal oskyldiga manniskor på en frukostservering... Hur reagerar de som overlever eller de anhoriga till de som mordats av en slump?

programme.title: Palo Alto
programme.desc: High School-eleverna Teddy, April, Fred och Emily ar som alla andra på jakt efter något att gora i Palo Altos tråkiga forortsmiljo. April ar vilsen och dras mellan en attraktion till sin aldre fotbollstranare och en oskuldsfull foralskelse i Teddy – en strulig skejtare vars kompis Fred bojar tappa greppet. Den lika vilsna Emily anvander istallet sex for att få bekraftelse.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Dont Come Knocking
programme.desc: Hollywoodstjarnan Howard Spence (Sam Shepard) har sett battre dagar. Han vilar på sina lagrar och lever på sin gamla stjarnstatus. Efter ytterligare en natt med vilda utsvavningar flyr han från inspelningen av nasta vasternfilm och rider ut på prarien och de stora vidderna precis som en av hjaltarna som han så ofta har gestaltat. Han soker tillflykt hemma hos sin mamma (Eva Marie Saint) som han inte har traffat på många år. Men inte ens dar stannar han sarskilt lange, for han får veta att han någonstans kan ha en son som han inte visste fanns. For Howard kanns det som en strimma hopp och ett bevis for att inte har levt sitt liv forgaves.

programme.title: Varg
programme.desc: Varg ar en storslagen film om Klemens (Peter Stormare) och hans systerson Nejla som lever mitt i det norrlandska landskapet på gransen mellan Sverige och Norge.

programme.title: Proxima
programme.desc: Sarah ar en fransk astronaut, och den enda kvinnliga deltagaren i det rymdprogram som forbereder sig infor en ett år lång expedition. Som ensamstående mamma till en åttaåring kanns expeditionen an mer kravande, och med lika delar skuld och mod forsoker hon hitta balans i sin roll som banbrytare och mamma.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: Dinner Rush
programme.desc: Dinner Rush utspelar sig under vad som från borjan inte tycks vara något annat an en helt vanlig jaktig kvall på Louis Cropas (Danny Aiello) populara restaurang Gigino i det fashionabla TriBeCa-kvarteret i New York. En gång var trattorian en enkel familjerestaurang men nu har den forvandlats till kvarterets mesta innekrog, stallet dar alla vill bli sedda. Detta mycket tack vare krogaren Cropas son Udos (Edoardo Ballerini) innovativa matlagningskonst som kommit att bli stallets kannetecken. Och just den har kvallen ar restaurangen som ett kalejdoskop av livet i dagens New York...

programme.title: Runaway Jury
programme.desc: Från mastaren John Grisham kommer en thriller med Dustin Hoffman, Gene Hackman, John Cusack och Rachel Weisz. En jury-fixare spelar ett dodligt katt-och-råtta-spel med en jurymedlem och en mystisk framling som båda erbjuder att "leverera" domen till hogstbjudande. Snart står både liv och miljoner på spel i en pulshojare full av ovantade vandningar.

programme.title: Jimmy P.
programme.desc: En orolig indianveteran bildar en exceptionell vanskap med en fransk psykoanalytiker nar de forsoker hitta botemedel mot deras lidande.

programme.title: Fast Girls
programme.desc: Nar kaxiga och gatsmarta Shania (Lenora Crichlow) traffar den ambitiosa medelklasstjejen Lisa (Lily James) kolliderar deras två varldar på loparbanan med explosiva foljder. De två sprintertjejerna kampar for att kvala in till VM i friidrott och moter tuffa motgångar och bitter rivalitet på sin dramatiska, hjartevarmande och inspirerande resa.

programme.title: Man on Fire
programme.desc: MAN ON FIRE ar en gripande thriller med Oscar® belonade Denzel Washington i huvudrollen. Han spelar Creasy, en f.d. utbrand CIA agent som tappat livsgnistan. Creasy overtalas av sin van Rayburn (Christopher Walken) att skydda en tioårig flicka i Mexico City dar barnkidnappningar tillhor vardagen. Creasy kommer flickan nara och deras relation gor att han återfår viljan att leva. Nar hon sedan blir kidnappad tappar Creasy allt forstånd. Han ger sig ut på en vansinnesjakt for att finna henne och ingenting kan stoppa honom.

programme.title: Winged Creatures
programme.desc: På ett ogonblick forandras allt - hur går du vidare nar ditt liv slås i spillror? Det ar tidig morgon i Los Angeles, en psykopat skjuter besinningslost ihjal ett antal oskyldiga manniskor på en frukostservering... Hur reagerar de som overlever eller de anhoriga till de som mordats av en slump?

programme.title: Once Were Warriors
programme.desc: Hos familjen Heke finns ingen frid att tala om. Jake Heke blir våldsam nar han dricker, den ena sonen har gått med i ett gatugang och den andra står infor åtal. Mamman Beth och barnen står infor det svåra, men livsavgorande valet mellan att stanna kvar i en hopplos situation, och att slå sig fria. Once Were Warriors ar ett prisvinnande familjedrama om att bejaka sitt forflutna for att skapa sin framtid.

programme.title: Frozen River
programme.desc: Dagarna fore julafton på gransen mellan USA och Kanada, tvingas Ray Eddy ta saken i egna hander nar hennes man forsvinner med handpenningen till nya husvagnen. Hon finner motvilligt en ovantad kumpan i urinvånaren Lila Littlewolf, som forsorjer sig på att smuggla illegala invandrare over gransen. Frozen River ar ett kargt kriminaldrama som vann Grand Jury Prize nar den hade premiar på Sundance filmfestival 2008. Filmen nominerades aven till två Oscars.

programme.title: Unfaithful
programme.desc: Edward och Connie Sumner ar ett medelålders par som bor den amerikanska drommen i fororterna i New York City. Somende lyckligt gift med en åtta år gammal son, en hund och en hushållerska, ar Sumners tysta varld krossad nar en chans traffar en framling drar Connie till en affar som kan betyda mer an bara slutet på ett aktenskap. UNFAITHFUL ar en erotisk thriller om skuld och raseri som frågar några av de svåraste frågorna om alla relationer.

programme.title: Fast Girls
programme.desc: Nar kaxiga och gatsmarta Shania (Lenora Crichlow) traffar den ambitiosa medelklasstjejen Lisa (Lily James) kolliderar deras två varldar på loparbanan med explosiva foljder. De två sprintertjejerna kampar for att kvala in till VM i friidrott och moter tuffa motgångar och bitter rivalitet på sin dramatiska, hjartevarmande och inspirerande resa.

programme.title: Rules Dont Apply
programme.desc: I Hollywood 1958 uppstår attraktion mellan en skådespelerska (Lily Collins) och hennes chauffor (Alden Ehrenreich), vilket satter deras religiosa varderingar på prov och går stick i stav med chefen Howard Hughes (Warren Beatty) forbud mot deras relation. Rules Don’t Apply (baserad på en berattelse av Beatty och Bo Goldman) ar regisserad av Beatty och i rollistan ser vi stjarnor som Annette Bening och Matthew Broderick.

programme.title: Gringa
programme.desc: En olycklig tonårstjej rymmer till Mexiko for att hitta den pappa hon aldrig kant. Tillsammans lar de sig att en familj kan bli hel igen, aven om de bara har de bitar som saknas.

programme.title: Dont Come Knocking
programme.desc: Hollywoodstjarnan Howard Spence (Sam Shepard) har sett battre dagar. Han vilar på sina lagrar och lever på sin gamla stjarnstatus. Efter ytterligare en natt med vilda utsvavningar flyr han från inspelningen av nasta vasternfilm och rider ut på prarien och de stora vidderna precis som en av hjaltarna som han så ofta har gestaltat. Han soker tillflykt hemma hos sin mamma (Eva Marie Saint) som han inte har traffat på många år. Men inte ens dar stannar han sarskilt lange, for han får veta att han någonstans kan ha en son som han inte visste fanns. For Howard kanns det som en strimma hopp och ett bevis for att inte har levt sitt liv forgaves.

programme.title: Teen Spirit
programme.desc: Elle Fanning spelar Violet, en blyg tonåring som drommer om att fly sin hemstad och uppfylla sin drom att sjunga. Med hjalp från ovantat håll anmaler hon sig till en talangtavling som kommer satta hennes integritet, talang och ambition på prov. Ett soundtrack fullt med poplåtar ger en ny spinn på den klassiska Askungesagan.

programme.title: Dinner Rush
programme.desc: Dinner Rush utspelar sig under vad som från borjan inte tycks vara något annat an en helt vanlig jaktig kvall på Louis Cropas (Danny Aiello) populara restaurang Gigino i det fashionabla TriBeCa-kvarteret i New York. En gång var trattorian en enkel familjerestaurang men nu har den forvandlats till kvarterets mesta innekrog, stallet dar alla vill bli sedda. Detta mycket tack vare krogaren Cropas son Udos (Edoardo Ballerini) innovativa matlagningskonst som kommit att bli stallets kannetecken. Och just den har kvallen ar restaurangen som ett kalejdoskop av livet i dagens New York...

programme.title: Ljus i skymningen (Lights in the Dusk)
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om nattvakten Koistinen som forlorar jobbet, friheten och drommarna. Men till sist skonjer han en strimma hopp.

programme.title: Palo Alto
programme.desc: High School-eleverna Teddy, April, Fred och Emily ar som alla andra på jakt efter något att gora i Palo Altos tråkiga forortsmiljo. April ar vilsen och dras mellan en attraktion till sin aldre fotbollstranare och en oskuldsfull foralskelse i Teddy – en strulig skejtare vars kompis Fred bojar tappa greppet. Den lika vilsna Emily anvander istallet sex for att få bekraftelse.

programme.title: Undergods
programme.desc: En sci-fi-dystopi kryddad med svart humor om en varld med endast ett fåtal overlevande, som alla ar en aning trasiga på sitt satt. Den kafkaliknande miljon kombinerad med 2020-talets krossade drommar ger redan i sig tittaren gåshud. Filmen borjar med att två liksamlare går runt langs de odelagda gatorna och vid sidan av arbetet berattar om sina grusade drommar som drivit dem till det dystra nulaget.

programme.title: Man on Fire
programme.desc: MAN ON FIRE ar en gripande thriller med Oscar® belonade Denzel Washington i huvudrollen. Han spelar Creasy, en f.d. utbrand CIA agent som tappat livsgnistan. Creasy overtalas av sin van Rayburn (Christopher Walken) att skydda en tioårig flicka i Mexico City dar barnkidnappningar tillhor vardagen. Creasy kommer flickan nara och deras relation gor att han återfår viljan att leva. Nar hon sedan blir kidnappad tappar Creasy allt forstånd. Han ger sig ut på en vansinnesjakt for att finna henne och ingenting kan stoppa honom.

programme.title: Miss Potter
programme.desc: Hon har fascinerat generationer av lasare, men hennes liv var en hemlighet. Fram tills nu Beatrix Potter ar en ogift 30-årig kvinna i en tid då kvinnans framsta uppgift ar att gifta sig fornamt och veta sin plats. Ingen, och framforallt inte Beatrix familj, kan forstå att hon hellre vill rita och forfatta små berattelser om djur. Och helt tokigt går det nar hon moter den oerfarne forlaggaren Norman Wayne. Han foralskar sig hals over huvud i både Beatrix och i hennes unika sagor. Och han staller Beatrix infor ett omojligt uppdrag - hon måste frigora sig från sin kravande familj.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Police are led on a wild goose chase when the wife of a prominent banker is kidnapped. An entomologists unexpected discovery leads to a new suspect - and the realization that ordinary office equipment can leave extraordinary clues.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A cop is found dead. His wife first says the motive was robbery; then she tells police it was suicide.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A man is found dead in his home, and his ex-wife has a perfect alibi. To determine time of death, investigators need to know when the victim ate his last meal.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A woman who suffered from mental illness is found dead. Was it due to natural causes, suicide or murder?

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: The investigation into the kidnapping and rape of an 18-year-old Ohio woman is aided when the victim returns hours after the incident occurred. With her help, the police are able to track the assailant to his front door.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Police are dispatched to the scene of a shooting, and discover the victims husband is one of their own.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A woman disappeared along a California highway in 1991. Three years later, the case was solved when a mans refrigerated truck was looked upon with suspicion.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A 19-year-old woman was found dead in her car, the scene had been staged to make murder appear to be suicide

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Two men were murdered in their beds. The next night, arson destroyed a family planning clinic. Investigators find a link between the two separate crimes.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A woman convicted of killing her mother in a car fire is granted a new trial. An expert witness has a different opinion as to how the fire started and, if proven, would clear the woman of any culpability.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: When an elderly couple died in a suspicious house fire, their son became the prime suspect. Investigators turned to forensic science to determine if the fire had been set deliberately, or if it was an unfortunate accident.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: When hunters found a skull in a Texas canyon, police found bits of clothing, small bones and a strand of hair. A forensic artist reconstructed her face. Now all they had to do was find her killer.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A Native American woman was brutally killed in the desert of New Mexico, and the crime scene was rich in forensic evidence: tire tracks, shoe impressions and even the murder weapons.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: When a talented television news anchor is shot to death outside her home, it appears to be a crime of passion perpetrated by an obsessed fan.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A man riding a bicycle was fatally injured, and police believed he was the victim of a hit-and-run accident.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: After the murder of Seattle residents, evidence from the couples dog eventually ties a murderer to the scene.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: When the mail-order bride of a former army sergeant goes missing, investigators look into the deaths of the mans previous two wives.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A car carrying three men pulls up alongside another on an Alaskan highway and fires shots, leaving a passenger dead. One of the passengers in the killers car agrees to testify against his friends. The resulting trials dont end the carnage.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: In 1999, a 12-year-old was found murdered in her home in Minnesota. Despite a meticulous search of the home and an exhaustive investigation, police had no suspects.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: In the summer of 1986, Kathleen Lipscombs body was found on a deserted road outside of San Antonio.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: After 6-year-old Michelle Lee Dorr went missing, her father confessed to murdering her. But investigators soon poked holes in his story, leaving the case unsolved for 14 years.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: The police investigate when a severed leg is discovered among garbage. Conventional means of identifying the victim are impossible, leading investigators to rely on DNA, forensic anthropology and toxicology.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: In 1984, California firefighters battled ten arson fires in three weeks. When cigarettes and a scrap of paper connected the case to similar fires further north, the hunt was on for a dangerous pyromaniac.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A man tells police he shot an intruder who killed his wife. Forensic evidence disproves that story later on.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A woman is found dead in a ravine, but crucial crime scene evidence had been washed away by severe thunderstorms. Almost 20 years later, an old hat brought the killer to justice.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: When more than 700 Oregonians contracted food poisoning from a unique strain of salmonella in 1984, investigators uncovered a secret plot to influence local elections.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Prompted by news of a flight attendants brutal murder, the son of a previous victim contacts police.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: When police recovered the car of a missing man, they expected to find his body - but it wasnt there.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Janet Overton died suspiciously in 1988, and the investigation hit a dead end when the autopsy indicated no foul play was involved. A telephone tip and the sensitive nose of a forensic examiner indicated otherwise.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: When two women from the same town were murdered in the same way, police feared a serial killer was on the loose. At first they thought the victims had nothing in common until they found tiny clues linking them to the same man.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Police hoped the shoe impressions found at a crime scene would put their investigation back on track.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: When a victim is brutally murdered in his bed, investigators find a shoe impression in the mud outside.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: A behavioral profile caused the Baton Rouge Police Department to search for the wrong man. They might not have made an arrest had it not been for a DNA picture of the suspect painted by a molecular biologist.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: Exploring how an American hit single from 1966 -- "The Cheater" by Bob Kuban and the In-Men -- foreshadowed the demise of the groups lead singer, Walter Scott.

programme.title: Forensic Files
programme.desc: An investigation into the murder of Katie Poirier is stymied by the lack of a body. Finally, investigators use a single tooth found among some charred remains to identify her.

programme.title: Man Who Cried for Revenge
programme.desc: Davy Flanagan, a former Union officer who was part of an attempt to break out of a Confederate prison camp during the Civil War and suffered a blow to the head that left him with amnesia. Then a bounty hunter shows up to collect a bounty on his head as a deserter.

programme.title: Four Rode Out
programme.desc: A U.S. marshal sets out to bring in a Mexican bandit accused of killing his girlfriends father, but it turns out that theres more to the story than there first appears to be.

programme.title: The Sundowners
programme.desc: Brother is pitted against brother in this tale of feuding ranchers in the Old West.

programme.title: For a Book of Dollars
programme.desc: A bounty hunter named Amen is hired by a group of nuns to recover stolen money. However, the nuns turn out to be female desperadoes in disguise, plotting to retrieve the booty pillaged by the ruthless outlaw Catapult and his gang. Amen must navigate a world of deception, danger, and betrayal to complete the job.

programme.title: Guns Of The Revolution
programme.desc: In Mexico, a mad general is leading his own war against the Church.

programme.title: Buckskin Frontier
programme.desc: A railroad man and the owner of a freight line battle for control of a crucial mountain pass.

programme.title: Murieta!
programme.desc: The story of Joaquin Murrieta, a real life Mexican bandit who terrorized California with his gang of raiders and cutthroats during the first half of the 19th century. Some saw him as a murderous outlaw, others as the Mexican Robin Hood.

programme.title: Bury Me Not
programme.desc: Two women hide the surprising truth as a sheriff investigates a murder.

programme.title: Companeros!
programme.desc: A Swedish arms dealer and a Mexican peon team up to rescue the intellectual leader of the Revolutionary cause, while taking part in numerous misadventures along the way.

programme.title: Wyatt Earp S01E09-12
programme.desc: In one of televisions first adult Westerns, the famous marshal puts his life on the line to maintain order, first in Dodge City, Kan., then in Tombstone, Ariz.

programme.title: Stagecoach
programme.desc: A group of people traveling on a stagecoach find their journey complicated by the threat of Geronimo and learn something about each other in the process.

programme.title: Twice a Judas
programme.desc: After waking up with amnesia in the desert next to a dead man, Luke Barrett begins piecing together his past. A stranger in black reveals that Luke was hired to kill his own brother, Victor Barrett, a wealthy landowner. As Luke seeks the truth, a deadly confrontation looms, and his memory recovery brings both clarity and danger.

programme.title: The Ugly Ones
programme.desc: An escapee Mexican outlaw returns to his hometown, where he is sheltered from a tenacious bounty killer by the townspeople - who discover too late that he is a changed man.

programme.title: Incredible Rocky Mountain Race
programme.desc: An old man observes a boy bullying his playmates and treats him to a morality lesson. The man tells the story of the epic cross-country race between a young Mark Twain and his rival, Mike Fink.

programme.title: Bad Mans River
programme.desc: Robber Roy King loses his wife, Alicia, to revolutionary Montero. Despite their rivalry they collaborate in an attempt to rob the Mexican government of one million dollars.

programme.title: Rattler Kid
programme.desc: Falsely convicted for robbing an army treasury, Tony Garrett escapes prison and sets out to find the real criminals responsible. As he hunts for revenge, he faces dangers and uncovers dark truths, determined to clear his name and make the true culprits pay for their actions.

programme.title: Wyatt Earp S01E13-16
programme.desc: In one of televisions first adult Westerns, the famous marshal puts his life on the line to maintain order, first in Dodge City, Kan., then in Tombstone, Ariz.

programme.title: Kill Django... Kill First
programme.desc: In a mining town, Johnny MaGee clashes with banker Anthony Burton, who uses bandits and deceit to seize gold mines and control the economy. Partnering with an old miner, Johnny seeks justice, while navigating love, betrayal, and alliances. As tensions rise, a bounty hunter joins the fray, promising a final showdown against corruption.

programme.title: White Fang
programme.desc: The wolf dog, White Fang, aids a reporter, a fur trapper, a nun, a young Eskimo boy and his father of ridding a gold mining town of a sleazy crime lord in 1896 Yukon, Canada.

programme.title: Tepepa
programme.desc: In early 20th century Mexico, Tepepa, a revolutionary hero, is set to be executed by Cascorro’s men. Just as the firing squad prepares, Doctor Henry Price, an Englishman, arrives and saves Tepepa. However, Price’s true intentions are revealed when he coldly explains that he saved him only to have the pleasure of killing him himself.

programme.title: Five Guns West
programme.desc: Shalee Jethro (Dorothy Malone) helps her father run a desert stagecoach station.

programme.title: Cut-Throats Nine
programme.desc: A cavalry troop is escorting a wagonload of convicts on their way to prison through the mountains when they are attacked by a bandit gang. Only a sergeant, his beautiful young daughter, and an assortment of seven sadistic, murderous prisoners survive, and they are left without horses or a wagon. The sergeant must find a way to get his prisoners to their destination while protecting his daughter, watching out for the still-pursuing bandits, and trying to determine which prisoner is the man who raped and murdered his wife.

programme.title: Django the Bastard
programme.desc: A ghostlike stranger arrives to avenge a Civil War betrayal. Former Confederate officers who caused the massacre of their own unit begin to die one by one, as Django delivers chilling justice from beyond the grave.

programme.title: Boot Hill
programme.desc: Victims of oppressive town boss Honey are offered help by an unusual alliance of gunmen and circus performers.

programme.title: Gunsight Ridge
programme.desc: Stage line agent investigates a series of robberies by taking the job of a deputy sheriff in a border Arizona town.

programme.title: The Gay Cavalier
programme.desc: The Cisco Kid embarks on a dual mission: rescuing a girl from a marriage to a false suitor and tracking down outlaws who robbed a gold-carrying stage. His task becomes clearer when he discovers that the so-called wealthy suitor is secretly behind the robbery. Cisco must untangle love, deception, and crime to bring justice.

programme.title: The Gay Amigo
programme.desc: Mistaken for bandits, Cisco and Pancho are captured by the Captain, who releases them to track the real gang. Cisco discovers the true leaders are the editor and blacksmith. Using cunning, he sows distrust between them, gains the blacksmith’s trust, and joins the gang, setting up a trap to bring the criminals to justice.

programme.title: His Name Was Sam Walbash, But They Call Him Amen
programme.desc: A cruel and ruthless bandit kills a tavern owner who had ratted him out to the authorities.

programme.title: Djurado
programme.desc: Djurado is a gun-slinging professional gambler who struts into the small town of Silver Mine and wins half of the local saloon, the other part of which belongs to Barbara, whilst battling notorious outlaw Tucan.

programme.title: The Lonesome Trail
programme.desc: Johnny Rush, an Indian wars veteran, returns home to find his land seized by a cattle baron and his love engaged to the enemy. After a brutal fight leaves him unable to use his gun arm, Rush learns to wield a bow and arrow with deadly precision. Determined to reclaim his home and confront betrayal, he fights back against overwhelming odds.

programme.title: Dead are Countless
programme.desc: As a child, Johnny witnessed his father’s death at the hands of soldiers. Now an outlaw, he seeks revenge by killing soldiers whenever possible. Lieutenant Garringo is tasked with capturing Johnny and bringing him back alive. A dangerous game of cat and mouse ensues, with Garringo determined to fulfill his mission.

programme.title: Day After Tomorrow
programme.desc: Bespectacled bounty hunter Stan Ross arrives in Canyon City after a bank robbery and uncovers a web of corruption. Hired by banker Jefferson to hunt Mexican bandits, Stan learns the bandits were falsely accused and once worked with Jefferson. As Stan digs deeper, he faces betrayal, hidden alliances, and a dangerous grip on the city.

First, she rolls up some tender Meatballs in a Lemon-Egg Sauce featuring a secret ingredient: rice (shh!). programme.title: Day 6
programme.desc: After exploring Peru, Jalou has to get over her fear when she goes white water kayaking. In Thailand, Kevin is feeling the pressure.

programme.title: Day 7

programme.title: The Pagoda

programme.title: The Blazer

programme.desc: A 1970 K5 Chevrolet Blazer undergoes a transformation with new paint, interior, and a diesel engine conversion.

programme.title: Episode Eight
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Our Auto Expert S1 - "Episode Eight"
programme.desc: Mike and Nik review the 2021 Ford Mustang Mach-E. Nik predicts the Genesis G80 will challenge German manufacturers. He showcases the 2021 Mini GP and Polestar 2. Mike explores the 2021 Infiniti QX50.

programme.title: Episode Nine
programme.sub-title: S01 : E09 Our Auto Expert S1 - "Episode Nine"
programme.desc: Nik experiences Mercedes-Benzs concept for Avatar 2. Both Nik and Mike unveil top-performing cars for value. Nik reviews the 2021 Kia Telluride and 2021 Lexus IS. Mike introduces the Ford Mach-E 1400.

programme.title: Gary, Indiana
programme.sub-title: S02 : E14 Epic Exploring S2 - "Gary, Indiana"
programme.desc: Josh is back in Gary, Indiana, for a local exploring adventure. With friends, he visits a former bank, the memorial auditorium and Union Train Station.

programme.title: Zagreb
programme.desc: Epic Exploring: Going Local visits Zagreb, Croatia. Cody fires a canon from the old tower, explores a never finished University Hospital and a political school.

programme.title: Las Vegas
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Car Crews with Supercar Blondie S1 - "Las Vegas"
programme.desc: Supercar Blondie arrives in Las Vegas in a million dollar Lamborghini SVJ roadster. Taken under the wing of Patrick, founder of the Junkyard Pirates, Alex is brought into the rat rod world - home to American mavericks and outsiders.

programme.title: Miami
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Car Crews with Supercar Blondie S1 - "Miami"
programme.desc: Supercar Blondie is given the keys to a five million dollar Pagani Huayra L’Ultimo as she explores the sub-culture of lowriders with the seal of approval from Horacio Pagani himself. Will she be accepted into this tribe?

programme.title: Detroit
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Car Crews with Supercar Blondie S1 - "Detroit"
programme.desc: Supercar Blondie arrives in ‘Motor City’ in the dead of winter but given access to a half million dollar new Ford GT raises her spirits. Her goal is to learn more about muscle cars, born in Detroit, and her journey takes her in different directions.

programme.title: Brazil
programme.desc: The World’s best Brazilian rider opens the doors to his house to show how it all started and brings us to Mexico for the most famous urban race in the world.

programme.title: Argentina
programme.desc: Two talented Canadian brothers and pro MTB riders decide to go on a freeride trip together and choose to explore the remote desert of Argentina.

programme.title: South Africa
programme.sub-title: S03 : E06 MTB Heroes S3 - "South Africa"
programme.desc: We follow the fastest and most stylish female MTB pro rider in the world during a trip to South Africa where she will ride the best trails around Cape Town.

programme.title: Morgan
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Find Me A Classic S1 - "Morgan"
programme.desc: Mat’s demanding client Gordon is in search of a Morgan, but will he be able to find the ideal car for the right price?

programme.title: Citroen DS
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Find Me A Classic S1 - "Citroen DS"
programme.desc: Mat goes in search of a perfect Citroen DS for Leon, a man who has strong connections to the DS, and to France.

programme.title: Mini
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Find Me A Classic S1 - "Mini"
programme.desc: Mat Watson travels Europe on the trail of a very special 1960s Mini.

programme.title: Hawaii
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 The Travel Bug S2 - "Hawaii"
programme.desc: Hawaii is arguably the world’s best-known island holiday destination. It’s an adventure lover’s playground with volcanoes, mountains, diving, surfing and loads of other fun activities.

programme.title: Taiwan, Part I
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 The Travel Bug S2 - "Taiwan, Part I"
programme.desc: As far as cities go, Taipei is one of the most intense, chaotic and diverse metropolitan centres on earth. We learn about Taiwan’s turbulent history, take a look at the country’s unique culture and indulge in the famous street food.

programme.title: Taiwan, Part II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E05 The Travel Bug S2 - "Taiwan, Part II"
programme.desc: From the noise and chaos of Taipei, to the cities in the south west of the country. Here is a more traditional way of life, and a chance to explore more of Taiwan’s history before heading into the heart of the nation to see the Alishan mountains.

programme.title: 72 Charger SE Resurrected
programme.sub-title: S06 : E13 Graveyard Carz S6 - "72 Charger SE Resurrected"
programme.desc: Will and Alyssa struggle with the billboard graphic. Mark finishes a suspension and the car that started the show rolls again.

programme.title: Grin and Bear a ‘Cuda
programme.sub-title: S07 : E01 Graveyard Carz S7 - "Grin and Bear a ‘Cuda"
programme.desc: In the season 7 debut, its all about the Cudas. The ghouls get cracking on the infamous 71 Phantom Cuda and Mark gets three new Barracudas delivered.

programme.title: Operation Firepower?
programme.sub-title: S07 : E03 Graveyard Carz S7 - "Operation Firepower?"
programme.desc: Mark announces a top-secret project to the ghouls and Allysa surprises her dad, when she manages to get him his old car for Father’s Day

programme.title: Lisbon
programme.sub-title: S01 : E07 Running the World S1 - "Lisbon"
programme.desc: Brothers Max and Benj Cave undertake a run where they attempt to escape from Lisbon castle without using any conventional exit routes.

programme.title: Delhi
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Running the World S1 - "Delhi"
programme.desc: Parkour athletes Max and Benj Cave head to Delhi India to complete a treacherous final run challenge.

programme.title: Mexico City
programme.sub-title: S01 : E09 Running the World S1 - "Mexico City"
programme.desc: Brothers Max and Benj Cave race through an 18th century monastery on the outskirts of Mexico City and whoever rings the bell in the tower first wins.

programme.title: Episode 7
programme.desc: A young snowmobilers first ride into the backcountry spins out of control.

programme.title: Episode 8
programme.desc: Tim demands a lot of everyone around him, especially during a cave rescue - what he describes as "the worst kind of rescue possible".

programme.title: Andy Soucek - Bentley Continental
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Endurance - 24 Hours at Spa S1 - "Andy Soucek - Bentley Continental"
programme.desc: In this profile, we get to know Andy Soucek competing in the Bentley Continental at the 2018 Total 24 Hours of Spa race held at the Spa-Francorchamps circuit.

programme.title: Ahmad Al Harthy - Aston Martin Vantage
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Endurance - 24 Hours at Spa S1 - "Ahmad Al Harthy - Aston Martin Vantage"
programme.desc: In this profile, we get to know Ahmad Al Harthy competing in the Aston Martin Vantage at the 2018 Total 24 Hours of Spa race at the Spa-Francorchamps circuit.

programme.title: Albert Costa - Lexus RC F
